          <div class="cc-stats">
            <span><strong>Focus:</strong> Monagas North</span>
            <span><strong>Status:</strong> Closing deal (Q1 2026)</span>
          </div>
          <p>Closing in on first major production deal since U.S. captured Maduro, working in Monagas North areas. One of six entities authorized under GL 50A.</p>
          <p class="source-citation">Source: <a href="https://today.reuters.com/business/energy/chevron-shell-closing-first-big-oil-production-deals-venezuela-since-us-captured-2026-03-10/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reuters (Mar 2026)</a></p>
